<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Prayer for Lent 5</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Mar 26, 2015 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
A woman asked Jesus <br></br>
to heal her daughter, <br></br>
and Jesus said nothing.
</p>

 <p>
Pilate asked Jesus <br></br>
to defend himself, <br></br>
and Jesus said nothing.
</p>

 <p>
Yet the girl was healed, <br></br>
and Jesus went to the cross.
</p>

 <p>
Forgive me, Lord, <br></br>
for the sin of <br></br>
saying everything but <br></br>
doing nothing.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>


